<subSubSection pageId="61" pageNumber="62" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="61.[151,1437,504,1069]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[201,316,937,961]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
Species in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lowry &amp; Stoddart" authorityYear="2012" box="[449,615,937,961]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pakynidae" genus="Ultimachelium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[449,615,937,961]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Ultimachelium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were previously assigned to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stephensen" authorityYear="1925" box="[948,1106,937,961]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pakynidae" genus="Pachychelium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[948,1106,937,961]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Pachychelium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. In our view the old concept of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stephensen" authorityYear="1925" box="[181,339,973,997]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pakynidae" genus="Pachychelium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[181,339,973,997]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Pachychelium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a complex of three genera: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stephensen" authorityYear="1925" box="[677,835,973,997]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pakynidae" genus="Pachychelium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[677,835,973,997]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Pachychelium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the North Atlantic and North Pacific with one species in the deep-water tropics of north-eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[703,809,1009,1033]" name="Australia" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Australia</collectingCountry>
; 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lowry &amp; Stoddart" authorityYear="2012" box="[825,941,1009,1033]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pakynidae" genus="Smaraldia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[825,941,1009,1033]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Smaraldia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a monotypic genus currently confined to southern temperate 
<collectingCountry box="[372,478,1045,1069]" name="Australia" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Australia</collectingCountry>
; and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lowry &amp; Stoddart" authorityYear="2012" box="[536,702,1045,1069]" class="Malacostraca" family="Pakynidae" genus="Ultimachelium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Amphipoda" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[536,702,1045,1069]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Ultimachelium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in southern South America and the Antarctic.
</paragraph>
